query:
SELECT 
  DATE_FORMAT(dr.date, '%Y-%m-%d') as date,
  b.nameAr as branch,
  dr.cash,
  dr.network,
  dr.balance,
  dr.total,
  dr.isMatched,
  dr.unmatchReason
FROM dailyRevenues dr
JOIN branches b ON dr.branchId = b.id
ORDER BY dr.date DESC
LIMIT 20;
